Class Analyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • MainLogic.Analyzer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Analyzer
extends java.lang.Thread
    Analyzer represents the main functionality of this program and it's responsible for analyzing a full excel sheet according with user implemented rules or default ones.
